## Attribution Requirement

When using VeriPro under the MIT License, you must include visible attribution
in one of the following ways:

1. In your project's README or documentation:
   "Powered by VeriPro - https://github.com/your-org/veripro"

2. In your application's about page or footer:
   "Verification powered by VeriPro"

3. In any published materials referencing the verification:
   "Verified using VeriPro formal verification platform"
